data.description: Beautiful home with a spectacular low maintenance back yard in West El Paso. As you enter the home you are greeted by a beautiful chandelier, a spacious living and dining room with high ceilings, lots of windows to brighten up the room and beautiful tile floors. Plenty of room to cook for the whole family in the large kitchen with granite counter tops and tons of cabinet space. A fireplace in the family room, perfect for movie nights. Upstairs you have a spacious loft, and all three bedrooms. The master has a walk-in closet, full bath with a walk-in shower and a separate hot tub. The covered patio has an outdoor cooking area with bar seating around the counter and ceiling fans to keep cool. Large back yard with artificial turf for minimal maintenance!
